        <title>Optional Hands on Activity: Try a Diagnostic or Formative Assessment</title>
        <contents>&lt;p&gt;Select an assessment activity that you saw in either video that could support your students to improve their learning.  Conduct it with your learners and take notes to share your experience with others. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Select at least one assessment strategy&lt;/b&gt; described in either
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtu.be/sphhVIPzJR8?list=PLImUeO1ttx1biHp5fHul5PxtIUIQU-sDd" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;i&gt;ASRP - Teacher/Student Session Introduction&lt;/i&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="http://link.brightcove.com/services/player/bcpid799570851001?bckey=AQ~~,AAAABAIN5DE~,L2UmrJXAX4qnHP7MHeX0ndaX2i8TOwiL&amp;amp;bclid=794230318001&amp;amp;bctid=1123146148001" target="_blank"&gt;Assessing Learning in the Adult ESL Classroom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Conduct it with your learners&lt;/b&gt; in the next week or so.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Take notes on your experience to share &lt;/b&gt;with others later in the Course.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
